"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-lifestyle-travel-hotel-dame-des-arts-paris-review-rooftop-olympics-2024-b1154021.html\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the search feature\", \"from\": 7, \"to\": 25}, {\"ngram\": \"your consent\", \"from\": 35, \"to\": 47}, {\"ngram\": \"cookies\", \"from\": 92, \"to\": 99}, {\"ngram\": \"similar technologies\", \"from\": 103, \"to\": 123}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"search\", \"from\": 175, \"to\": 181}]}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our privacy policy\", \"from\": 187, \"to\": 205}, {\"ngram\": \"more information\", \"from\": 210, \"to\": 226}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Travel This stylish young hotel is the place to be for those visiting the city for Paris 2024 This summer,Pariswill be the city on everyone's lips.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 378, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 313, \"end\": 323, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.5483983943977416e-18, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This stylish young hotel\", \"from\": 236, \"to\": 260}, {\"ngram\": \"the place\", \"from\": 264, \"to\": 273}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 299, \"to\": 307}, {\"ngram\": \"Pariswill\", \"from\": 335, \"to\": 344}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 348, \"to\": 356}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone's lips\", \"from\": 360, \"to\": 375}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As millions descend on the capital from home and abroad, the city's streets, p\\u00e2tisseries andhotelswill be bursting at the seams like overstuffed pain au chocolats.\", \"from\": 379, \"to\": 542, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"millions\", \"from\": 382, \"to\": 390}, {\"ngram\": \"the capital\", \"from\": 402, \"to\": 413}, {\"ngram\": \"the city's streets\", \"from\": 436, \"to\": 454}, {\"ngram\": \"p\\u00e2tisseries andhotelswill\", \"from\": 456, \"to\": 481}, {\"ngram\": \"the seams\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 506}, {\"ngram\": \"overstuffed pain au chocolats\", \"from\": 512, \"to\": 541}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You will be hard pressed to find even a moment of calm amongst the Olympic madness.\", \"from\": 543, \"to\": 626, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"even a moment\", \"from\": 576, \"to\": 589}, {\"ngram\": \"calm\", \"from\": 593, \"to\": 597}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic madness\", \"from\": 606, \"to\": 625}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Or maybe you will not want to?\", \"from\": 627, \"to\": 657, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"H\\u00f4tel Dame des Arts, which opened on the Left Bank last year, is the perfect place to find a little bit of both.\", \"from\": 659, \"to\": 771, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 665, \"end\": 669, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Knight\", \"score\": 0.9999996684664988, \"rank\": 2.1491909695658782e-07, \"text\": \"Dame\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Knight\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Knight\"}, {\"begin\": 700, \"end\": 709, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rive_Gauche\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.275084915442102e-27, \"text\": \"Left Bank\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rive_Gauche\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rive_Gauche\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the perfect place\", \"from\": 724, \"to\": 741}, {\"ngram\": \"a little bit\", \"from\": 750, \"to\": 762}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The rooms and halls of this chic, design-focused hotel are a quiet, calming refuge, while its dinner and party spaces are delectable and lively.\", \"from\": 772, \"to\": 916, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The rooms\", \"from\": 772, \"to\": 781}, {\"ngram\": \"halls\", \"from\": 786, \"to\": 791}, {\"ngram\": \"this chic, design-focused hotel\", \"from\": 795, \"to\": 826}, {\"ngram\": \"a quiet, calming refuge\", \"from\": 831, \"to\": 854}, {\"ngram\": \"its dinner\", \"from\": 862, \"to\": 872}, {\"ngram\": \"party spaces\", \"from\": 877, \"to\": 889}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And that's not even mentioning its pi\\u00e8ce de r\\u00e9sistance: the rooftop, which is where everyone who's anyone in the City of Lights will want to be as soon as the temperature breaks into the 20s.\", \"from\": 917, \"to\": 1108, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its pi\\u00e8ce de r\\u00e9sistance\", \"from\": 948, \"to\": 971}, {\"ngram\": \"the rooftop\", \"from\": 973, \"to\": 984}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 1001, \"to\": 1009}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1022}, {\"ngram\": \"the City\", \"from\": 1026, \"to\": 1034}, {\"ngram\": \"Lights\", \"from\": 1038, \"to\": 1044}, {\"ngram\": \"the 20s\", \"from\": 1100, \"to\": 1107}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While many visit Paris for the traditional Haussmannian, bouillabaisse-based, Sex in the City season six fantasy, this hotel is what cool, young Paris actually feels like, despite being so centrally located.\", \"from\": 1110, \"to\": 1317, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1127, \"end\": 1132, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4146866874976708e-32, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1249, \"end\": 1260, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Young_Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999989076969, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"young Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Young_Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Young_Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the City season\", \"from\": 1195, \"to\": 1210}, {\"ngram\": \"six fantasy\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1222}, {\"ngram\": \"this hotel\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1234}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dame des Arts is within a short sprint ofNotre Dame, as well as its gothic sister the Sainte-Chapelle, and the Seine.\", \"from\": 1318, \"to\": 1435, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1318, \"end\": 1322, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Knight\", \"score\": 0.9999996684664988, \"rank\": 2.1491909695658782e-07, \"text\": \"Dame\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Knight\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Knight\"}, {\"begin\": 1429, \"end\": 1434, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.352012887756023e-28, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a short sprint ofNotre Dame\", \"from\": 1342, \"to\": 1369}, {\"ngram\": \"its gothic sister\", \"from\": 1382, \"to\": 1399}, {\"ngram\": \"the Sainte-Chapelle\", \"from\": 1400, \"to\": 1419}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The jury's still out as to whether events will be allowed to happen in the Seine during theOlympics(will it be clean enough?\", \"from\": 1437, \"to\": 1561, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1512, \"end\": 1517, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.352012887756023e-28, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The jury\", \"from\": 1437, \"to\": 1445}, {\"ngram\": \"events\", \"from\": 1472, \"to\": 1478}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us leave that to the professionals to find out) but if they are, you are in plum position to pop down early and get a spot on the riverside.\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1706, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1566, \"to\": 1568}, {\"ngram\": \"the professionals\", \"from\": 1583, \"to\": 1600}, {\"ngram\": \"plum position\", \"from\": 1642, \"to\": 1655}, {\"ngram\": \"a spot\", \"from\": 1682, \"to\": 1688}, {\"ngram\": \"the riverside\", \"from\": 1692, \"to\": 1705}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It may not be located in the trendy ninth, 10th or 18th arrondissement, but for an Olympics summer, would you even want it to be?\", \"from\": 1708, \"to\": 1837, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the trendy ninth, 10th or 18th arrondissement\", \"from\": 1733, \"to\": 1778}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympics summer\", \"from\": 1788, \"to\": 1806}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You are smack bang in the middle of the action, and not far from the Jardins du Luxembourg or des Plaintes, for some more relaxing park sunbathing.\", \"from\": 1838, \"to\": 1985, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1918, \"end\": 1928, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luxembourg\", \"score\": 0.9997029560248666, \"rank\": 0.0002971322365139459, \"text\": \"Luxembourg\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luxembourg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luxembourg\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"smack bang\", \"from\": 1846, \"to\": 1856}, {\"ngram\": \"the middle\", \"from\": 1860, \"to\": 1870}, {\"ngram\": \"the action\", \"from\": 1874, \"to\": 1884}, {\"ngram\": \"des Plaintes\", \"from\": 1932, \"to\": 1944}, {\"ngram\": \"some more relaxing park sunbathing\", \"from\": 1950, \"to\": 1984}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Plus, you are surrounded by metro stations, with Saint-Michel Notre-Dame station just 50 metres away, Built in 1959, H\\u00f4tel Dame des Arts' is a spring chicken compared to many of its distinguished neighbours.\", \"from\": 1986, \"to\": 2194, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2035, \"end\": 2047, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Michael_in_the_Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 0.9999999459591905, \"rank\": 5.404081600023497e-08, \"text\": \"Saint-Michel\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Michael_in_the_Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Michael_in_the_Catholic_Church\"}, {\"begin\": 2048, \"end\": 2058, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Notre-Dame_de_Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4980010063244613e-24, \"text\": \"Notre-Dame\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Notre-Dame_de_Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Notre-Dame_de_Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"metro stations\", \"from\": 2014, \"to\": 2028}, {\"ngram\": \"H\\u00f4tel Dame des Arts\", \"from\": 2103, \"to\": 2122}, {\"ngram\": \"a spring chicken\", \"from\": 2127, \"to\": 2143}, {\"ngram\": \"its distinguished neighbours\", \"from\": 2164, \"to\": 2192}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In keeping, its decor feels fresh and stylish yet grown up.\", \"from\": 2195, \"to\": 2254, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"keeping\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2205}, {\"ngram\": \"its decor\", \"from\": 2207, \"to\": 2216}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dame des Arts does not need to oversell with bold colours or prints, it's all muted hues and thoughtful, low lighting, brought to balance with a sunlight flooded courtyard and rooftop.\", \"from\": 2255, \"to\": 2439, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2255, \"end\": 2259, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Knight\", \"score\": 0.9999996684664988, \"rank\": 2.1491909695658782e-07, \"text\": \"Dame\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Knight\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Knight\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"bold colours\", \"from\": 2300, \"to\": 2312}, {\"ngram\": \"prints\", \"from\": 2316, \"to\": 2322}, {\"ngram\": \"all muted hues\", \"from\": 2329, \"to\": 2343}, {\"ngram\": \"thoughtful, low lighting\", \"from\": 2348, \"to\": 2372}, {\"ngram\": \"a sunlight\", \"from\": 2398, \"to\": 2408}, {\"ngram\": \"courtyard\", \"from\": 2417, \"to\": 2426}, {\"ngram\": \"rooftop\", \"from\": 2431, \"to\": 2438}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The walls are panelled in light wood and the palette is neutral without being greige.\", \"from\": 2440, \"to\": 2525, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The walls\", \"from\": 2440, \"to\": 2449}, {\"ngram\": \"light wood\", \"from\": 2466, \"to\": 2476}, {\"ngram\": \"the palette\", \"from\": 2481, \"to\": 2492}, {\"ngram\": \"greige\", \"from\": 2518, \"to\": 2524}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many of the seats in its lobby and dining area are rounded booths, so couples can sit comfortably together.\", \"from\": 2527, \"to\": 2634, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the seats\", \"from\": 2535, \"to\": 2544}, {\"ngram\": \"its lobby and dining area\", \"from\": 2548, \"to\": 2573}, {\"ngram\": \"rounded booths\", \"from\": 2578, \"to\": 2592}, {\"ngram\": \"couples\", \"from\": 2597, \"to\": 2604}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The rooftop echoes the colours of Paris' cityscape, letting the colourful drinks and guests' outfits speak for themselves.\", \"from\": 2635, \"to\": 2757, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2669, \"end\": 2674, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4146866874976708e-32, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The rooftop\", \"from\": 2635, \"to\": 2646}, {\"ngram\": \"the colours\", \"from\": 2654, \"to\": 2665}, {\"ngram\": \"the colourful drinks\", \"from\": 2695, \"to\": 2715}, {\"ngram\": \"guests' outfits\", \"from\": 2720, \"to\": 2735}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Oh, and it's got the most stylish ashtrays you have ever seen.\", \"from\": 2758, \"to\": 2820, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Apparently many non-smoking guests buy them just to put their house keys in.\", \"from\": 2821, \"to\": 2897, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many non-smoking guests\", \"from\": 2832, \"to\": 2855}, {\"ngram\": \"their house keys\", \"from\": 2877, \"to\": 2893}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am still kicking myself for forgetting to stash one in my luggage.\", \"from\": 2898, \"to\": 2966, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my luggage\", \"from\": 2955, \"to\": 2965}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While Dame des Arts does offer a few Eiffel Tower-view rooms and suites, the small rooms are perfectly formed.\", \"from\": 2968, \"to\": 3078, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2974, \"end\": 2978, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Knight\", \"score\": 0.9999996684664988, \"rank\": 2.1491909695658782e-07, \"text\": \"Dame\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Knight\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Knight\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a few Eiffel Tower-view rooms\", \"from\": 2999, \"to\": 3028}, {\"ngram\": \"suites\", \"from\": 3033, \"to\": 3039}, {\"ngram\": \"the small rooms\", \"from\": 3041, \"to\": 3056}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dame des Arts makes great use of small spaces in each of its 109 rooms, and even its 12 square metre classic rooms feel roomy and perfectly intimate.\", \"from\": 3079, \"to\": 3228, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3079, \"end\": 3083, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Knight\", \"score\": 0.9999996684664988, \"rank\": 2.1491909695658782e-07, \"text\": \"Dame\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Knight\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Knight\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"great use\", \"from\": 3099, \"to\": 3108}, {\"ngram\": \"small spaces\", \"from\": 3112, \"to\": 3124}, {\"ngram\": \"its 109 rooms\", \"from\": 3136, \"to\": 3149}, {\"ngram\": \"even its 12 square metre classic rooms\", \"from\": 3155, \"to\": 3193}, {\"ngram\": \"roomy\", \"from\": 3199, \"to\": 3204}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In each room, you will find ecru and heather padded headboards accompanying luxuriously large beds, Diptyque toiletries and some of the most aesthetically pleasing hotel bathrooms you may ever set eyes on.\", \"from\": 3230, \"to\": 3435, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"each room\", \"from\": 3233, \"to\": 3242}, {\"ngram\": \"ecru\", \"from\": 3258, \"to\": 3262}, {\"ngram\": \"luxuriously large beds\", \"from\": 3306, \"to\": 3328}, {\"ngram\": \"the most aesthetically pleasing hotel bathrooms\", \"from\": 3362, \"to\": 3409}, {\"ngram\": \"eyes\", \"from\": 3427, \"to\": 3431}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Anyone looking into a London bathroom renovation: take note, this is how you style a small space.\", \"from\": 3436, \"to\": 3533, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3458, \"end\": 3464, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999999931788, \"rank\": 6.643044011046912e-12, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Anyone\", \"from\": 3436, \"to\": 3442}, {\"ngram\": \"note\", \"from\": 3491, \"to\": 3495}, {\"ngram\": \"a small space\", \"from\": 3519, \"to\": 3532}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While the party might be well-publicised as being at the (roof)top of the hotel, the bottom floor is just as worthy of a visit, if not more.\", \"from\": 3535, \"to\": 3675, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the party\", \"from\": 3541, \"to\": 3550}, {\"ngram\": \"the (roof)top\", \"from\": 3588, \"to\": 3601}, {\"ngram\": \"the hotel\", \"from\": 3605, \"to\": 3614}, {\"ngram\": \"the bottom floor\", \"from\": 3616, \"to\": 3632}, {\"ngram\": \"a visit\", \"from\": 3654, \"to\": 3661}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The restaurant, offering elevated Mexican cuisine is ideal if you are looking for an alternative to classic French dining, especially if you are looking to try an original fusion, as it blends Mexican, French and pan Asian.\", \"from\": 3676, \"to\": 3899, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3710, \"end\": 3725, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexican_cuisine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mexican cuisine\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexican_cuisine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexican_cuisine\"}, {\"begin\": 3784, \"end\": 3790, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.999700679080534, \"rank\": 0.0002994016227593613, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 3869, \"end\": 3876, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexican_cuisine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2114376232989105e-21, \"text\": \"Mexican\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexican_cuisine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexican_cuisine\"}, {\"begin\": 3878, \"end\": 3884, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.999700679080534, \"rank\": 0.0002994016227593613, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 3893, \"end\": 3898, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_cuisine\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.835728172804779e-12, \"text\": \"Asian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_cuisine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_cuisine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The restaurant\", \"from\": 3676, \"to\": 3690}, {\"ngram\": \"an alternative\", \"from\": 3758, \"to\": 3772}, {\"ngram\": \"an original fusion\", \"from\": 3836, \"to\": 3854}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The flavours work perfectly together, bringing out power in even the simplest dishes.\", \"from\": 3900, \"to\": 3985, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The flavours\", \"from\": 3900, \"to\": 3912}, {\"ngram\": \"power\", \"from\": 3951, \"to\": 3956}, {\"ngram\": \"even the simplest dishes\", \"from\": 3960, \"to\": 3984}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Classics such as guacamole are given more delicate tasting notes, and the red tuna and seabream tostadas are as good as it gets.\", \"from\": 3986, \"to\": 4114, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Classics\", \"from\": 3986, \"to\": 3994}, {\"ngram\": \"guacamole\", \"from\": 4003, \"to\": 4012}, {\"ngram\": \"more delicate tasting notes\", \"from\": 4023, \"to\": 4050}, {\"ngram\": \"the red tuna\", \"from\": 4056, \"to\": 4068}, {\"ngram\": \"seabream tostadas\", \"from\": 4073, \"to\": 4090}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is nothing - nothing - quite like the corn tempura, though.\", \"from\": 4115, \"to\": 4180, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 4124, \"to\": 4131}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 4134, \"to\": 4141}, {\"ngram\": \"the corn tempura\", \"from\": 4155, \"to\": 4171}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I would buy a whole Eurostar ticket just to get back to that dish.\", \"from\": 4181, \"to\": 4247, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4201, \"end\": 4209, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"score\": 0.999999999996362, \"rank\": 3.75904501277098e-12, \"text\": \"Eurostar\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that dish\", \"from\": 4237, \"to\": 4246}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And with every punch the food packs, the drinks rise up to meet it.\", \"from\": 4249, \"to\": 4316, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"every punch\", \"from\": 4258, \"to\": 4269}, {\"ngram\": \"the food packs\", \"from\": 4270, \"to\": 4284}, {\"ngram\": \"the drinks\", \"from\": 4286, \"to\": 4296}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Enjoy a perfect Pamela, followed by a floral French spritz.\", \"from\": 4317, \"to\": 4376, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4333, \"end\": 4339, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pamela_Rebecca_Barnes\", \"score\": 0.9883051105652552, \"rank\": 0.011833252912236322, \"text\": \"Pamela\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pamela_Rebecca_Barnes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pamela_Rebecca_Barnes\"}, {\"begin\": 4362, \"end\": 4368, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.999700679080534, \"rank\": 0.0002994016227593613, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The daring can even pair a shot of tequila with their pudding of lime and jalapeno sorbets.\", \"from\": 4377, \"to\": 4468, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The daring\", \"from\": 4377, \"to\": 4387}, {\"ngram\": \"a shot\", \"from\": 4402, \"to\": 4408}, {\"ngram\": \"tequila\", \"from\": 4412, \"to\": 4419}, {\"ngram\": \"their pudding\", \"from\": 4425, \"to\": 4438}, {\"ngram\": \"lime and jalapeno sorbets\", \"from\": 4442, \"to\": 4467}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It works, trust me.\", \"from\": 4469, \"to\": 4488, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Anyone looking for a young, fun weekend break withou